OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FThe daughter of footballer Joe
OL,7,FThompson, who died last month aged
OL,8,Fjust 36, has said he was the 'best
OL,9,Fdad' who just 'loved to help people'.
OL,11,FLula Thompson 12, described the
OL,12,FRochdale star as 'funny' and
OL,13,F'positive' and said she had 'so many
OL,14,Fspecial memories' of their time
OL,15,Ftogether.
OL,17,FJoe died in April after being
OL,18,Fdiagnosed three times with cancer.
