OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FJoe was a legend at his former club
OL,7,FRochdale and respected across the
OL,8,Fsporting community for the way in
OL,9,Fwhich he faced adversity and for his
OL,10,Ffundraising.
OL,12,FHis family have issued an open
OL,13,Finvitation to his supporters to attend
OL,14,Fhis funeral on May 12, saying it was
OL,15,FJoe's wishes to have a big crowd there
OL,16,Fto say goodbye.
OL,18,FHis wife Chantelle described Joe as
OL,19,F"an incredible man" whose "heart was
OL,20,Fhumongous".
