OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Granada's sports
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Mike Hall, she said Joe
OL,8,Fwas "thoughtful and passionate", an
OL,9,Famazing dad, husband and brother, and
OL,10,Fsomeone who "lit up the room".
OL,12,FShe said he was "full of positivity,
OL,13,Feven until the very last day".
OL,15,FChantelle added: "People say we've had
OL,16,Fsome tough times, which we have - with
OL,17,Fthe three cancer diagnoses, we lost
OL,18,Fbaby Dre in 2021 but even throughout
OL,19,Fthose times we've managed to make the
OL,20,Fbest of the situations and we've made
OL,21,Fsome incredible memories.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
