OL,6,F"And I think we wouldn't maybe have
OL,7,Fbeen as focussed on spending time
OL,8,Ftogether and creating those memories
OL,9,Fif it wasn't for the diagnoses at the
OL,10,Fstart because that kind of made us
OL,11,Frealise life is too short to not be
OL,12,Fdoing that."
OL,14,FJoe was first diagnosed with Hodgkin
OL,15,Flymphoma in 2013 and recovered before
OL,16,Fthe cancer returned in 2017. He went
OL,17,Fon to recover a second time.
