OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FJoe revealed in March last year that
OL,7,Fhe had stage four lymphoma which had
OL,8,Fspread to his lungs. He died in April
OL,9,Fwith his family beside him.
OL,11,FHis career started at Manchester
OL,12,FUnited and ended in Rochdale where in
OL,13,F2018, he scored the goal which kept
OL,14,Fthe club in the Football League,
OL,15,Fearning him legendary status.
OL,17,FLula said she still believes her dad
OL,18,Fis with her.
