OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FShe recounted how she'd been on a walk
OL,7,Fjust a week after her dad had passed
OL,8,Faway and after asking for a sign, had
OL,9,Flooked down to find a row of feathers
OL,10,Fon the ground..
OL,12,FLula talks about the signs she
OL,13,Fbelieves her dad sent her:
OL,15,FJoe's funeral will take place on
OL,16,FMonday 12 May at St Mark's Church in
OL,17,FWorsley. His family have issued an
OL,18,Fopen invitation for anyone to attend.
OL,20,F"It was Joe's wishes," Chantelle said.
