OL,6,F"We spoke about this prior to him
OL,7,Fpassing. He said he wanted anyone who
OL,8,Ffelt he had impacted them in any way
OL,9,Fwhether by football, personally or
OL,10,Fwork.
OL,12,F"He didn't want it to be a closed
OL,13,Ffuneral. A little bit of his ego would
OL,14,Flove to see a lot of people there."
